title: Launch In Victory // Launch In Victory (Part 4) // Michael Todd
description: Week 4 of our series Launch In Victory started with a bang! Our lead pastor, Michael Todd, is back, and he’s teaching us everything we need to launch something in all of our lives. What is God wanting to launch in your life? Take that step. Start that project. Write that song. If God is calling you to it, He will help you through it. Let this series be a launching pad for whatever God is starting in your life. Let us know what God is launching in your life, and share this message with a friend!
